high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the metal spoon that is in the sink.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Place the metal spoon handle down inside the mug that is in the sink.
Pick up the mug with the metal spoon in it.
Turn around and begin walking forward, then hang a right and continue straight, turn right at the table and face the black shelving unit.
Place the mug with the metal spoon in it on top of the metal shelving unit behind the sweet potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a spoon in it on top of a shelving unit.

high_descs: Go to the sink on the right.
Take the spoon from the sink.
Go to the right side of the sink.
Put the spoon in the mug in the sink.
Take the mug from the sink.
Go to the black stand to the left of the sink counter.
Put the mug on the top right corner of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on a stand.

high_descs: Move to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the sink.
Move over to the right towards the mug in the sink.
Put the spoon in the mug.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Bring the mug to the black table.
Put the mug on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put the spoon with mug on the black table.
